+ *					also 1 - 6)
+ *	vendor=0xVVVV		Default 0x0525 (NetChip), USB Vendor ID
+ *	product=0xPPPP		Default 0xa4a5 (FSG), USB Product ID
+ *	release=0xRRRR		Override the USB release number (bcdDevice)
