+ <td> Read</td>
+ </tr>
+
+ <tr>
+ <td> lpm_response </td>
+ <td> Gets or sets lpm_response mode. Applicable only in device mode.
+ <td> Write</td>
+ </tr>
+
+ <tr>
+ <td> sleep_status </td>
+ <td> Shows sleep status of device.
+ <td> Read</td>
+ </tr>
+
+ </table>
+
