+ </td></tr>
+
+<tr>
+ <td>ahb_thr_ratio</td>
+ <td>Specifies AHB Threshold ratio.
+ - Values: 0 to 3 (default 0)
+ </td></tr>
+
+<tr>
+ <td>power_down</td>
+ <td>Specifies Power Down(Hibernation) Mode.
